<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>Verify Your Account</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
    .button { display: inline-block; padding: 10px 20px; background-color: #007bff; color: #fff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; }
    .footer { margin-top: 20px; font-size: 12px; color: #777; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Welcome to AutoMotive_Industry!</h1>
    <p>Hi {{name}},</p>
    <p>Thank you for signing up for AutoMotive_Industry! To complete your registration, please use the following OTP to verify your email address:</p>
    <p><strong style="font-size: 24px; letter-spacing: 2px;">{{otp}}</strong></p>
    <p>This OTP will expire in 1 minute for security reasons.</p>
    <p>If you didn't create an account with AutoMotive_Industry, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
    <p>Best regards,<br>The AutoMotive_Industry Team</p>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; 2025 AutoMotive_Industry. All rights reserved.</p>
      <p>If you have any questions, please contact our support team.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>